{
  "texts": [
    "Key radiobiological factors, such as DNA repair capacity and mechanisms, are pivotal in the modeling process, considering the decreasing dose rate pattern in RPT.",
    "This pattern affects biological processes like redistribution, repopulation, and adaptive response, necessitating their incorporation into TDT models [74].",
    "Additionally, tumor vasculature and oxygen status are crucial elements for a comprehensive representation of radiobiological complexities in personalized TDTs [75].",
    "Immunological data Radiopharmaceuticalscan activate immunological pathways crucial for RPT success [78].",
    "These pathways modulate the immune response in both tumor and normal tissues, affecting clinical outcomes [79]."
  ]
}